  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.42,
    "endTime": 143.6,
    "text": "And I'm so sorry again, tried to get here as soon as I could, but it is taking forever to paint my new apartment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.695,
    "endTime": 145.9,
    "text": "No, I'm in the same f*cking (place)!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.17,
    "endTime": 150.2,
